      <h1>1966 Porsche 912</h1>
      <p class="dek">
        A numbers-matching 912 coupe that spent roughly thirty years parked in the eastern Washington desert
        before coming home for a mechanical and metal revival — including a reunion with the same shop that
        serviced it half a century earlier.
      </p>
