        <h2>What's been done — roughly the past eight years</h2>
        <p>
          All of the following happened under Rusty's ownership, roughly the past eight years: the Akers
          Porsche mechanical work above, a full sill and front-passenger-fender metal repair with repaint —
          documented start to finish, April 28 through May 30, 2020 — and a fuel pump rebuild among other
          smaller items.
        </p>

