        <h2>The car today</h2>
        <p>
          Back together, running, and out at shows — a driver in the true sense, even with the mileage kept
          low. The original wood-and-aluminum wheel is still on the car.
        </p>
        <div class="callout auth">
          <b>Open detail — wheels:</b> currently wearing a set of Fuchs alloys, correct to the car — just not
